# Synapse/CT liver thin/SegTHOR/Lung Cancer Dataset Handler

This repository contains tools for processing the BraTS brain tumor segmentation dataset. Due to the large size of the dataset, it is not included in this repository. Follow the instructions below to download and prepare the data.

